 ${python3:Depends},
 snapd
Description: LXD-based sandboxes for running AI tools safely on Ubuntu
 ailab creates LXD sandboxes that are pre-wired to use AI services running on
 the host while keeping installed software isolated from the rest of the
 system. Each container shares the user's home directory so files remain
 directly accessible on the host.
 .
 This package depends on snapd, installs the lxd snap during package
 configuration if needed, and installs the lemonade-server snap only when
 lemonade-server is not already installed via snap or Debian package.
